Methods exist for check objects with a single canonical plot (one object
class maps to one figure). Object types that can be plotted several different
ways — an aniframe, which feeds both \code{\link[=plot_trajectory]{plot_trajectory()}} and
\code{\link[=plot_timeseries]{plot_timeseries()}} — deliberately do not have a single method, since there
